    "Dialect spoken.",
    "The Table 1d shows the distribution of students in terms of their dialect.",
    "It exemplifies that majority of students are Ilocanos.",
    "Ilocano is the mother tongue of 42 students or 93.3 percent which top among the other two dialects which are Ybanag and Tagalog.",
    "This finding indicates that the population of Grade-10 class of Ipil National High School is dominated by students whose native language is Ilocano despite the school is situated at the hillside."
  ]
}